"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua"	"Demonic Summoning[CHC]"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_Description"	"Summon a Eidolon at the expense of your own life. The Eidolon has the ability Void Bolt. If the Eidolon has been summoned, it will be fully healed and its duration will be extended.<br><br>For every %upgrade_kill_count% creeps killed by the Eidolon, Enigma gains one stack of Demon Mastery. If the Eidolon kills an enemy hero, Enigma directly gains %hero_kill_upgrade% stacks of Demon Mastery.<br><br>Each stack of Demon Mastery levels up the Eidolon, increasing its %mana_regen% Mana Regeneration and %health_gain% Health, and enhancing the Eidolon's abilities.<br><br>Upon death of either Enigma or the Eidolon, %death_lose% stacks of Demon Mastery are lost."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_Lore"	"Enigma is capable of drawing aspects of himself from other dimensions - the result is a trio of dark eidolons that hunt the corporeal plane."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_eidelon_max_health"	"EIDOLON HP:"
